                            <comment id="397371" author="adilger" created="Tue, 19 Dec 2023 04:08:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16057&quot; title=&quot;OBD_MD_FLGROUP not set for ladvise rpc&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16057&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16057&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch was included in 2.15.53.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="393324" author="gerrit" created="Fri, 17 Nov 2023 00:04:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;&quot;Andriy Skulysh &amp;lt;andriy.skulysh@hpe.com&amp;gt;&quot; uploaded a new patch:&lt;/del&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53161&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53161&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;del&gt;Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15695&quot; title=&quot;dt_ladvise(): ASSERTION( dt-&amp;gt;do_body_ops-&amp;gt;dbo_ladvise )&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15695&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15695&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; osd: dt_ladvise(): ASSERTION( dt&lt;/del&gt;&amp;gt;do_body_ops-&amp;gt;dbo_ladvise)-&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;del&gt;Project: fs/lustre-release&lt;/del&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
